#: lib/help.php:412
msgid ""
"LEVEL : level of severity (<code>CRITICAL</code>, <code>HIGH</code> or "
"<code>MEDIUM</code>), information (<code>INFO</code>, <code>UPLOAD</code>) "
"and debugging mode (<code>DEBUG_ON</code>)."
